ldn't leave them with mother-in-law. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6752774 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 When your children had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14290744 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 No. Couldn't afford it. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6752774 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 Do you remember anything you did with your husband and children on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14290744 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 Only just - just an ordinary - just an ordinary day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6752774 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 You wouldn't be able to afford presents or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14290744 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6752774 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 It was just a day's holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14290744 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 That's right, yes. I just - if I'd got about four or five shilling to spare they had a big toy
 shop in Hanley, well I could have got all the lot of them a little something - and they appreciated - put them an apple and orange in a stocking and a bar of chocolate, and they thought about it just as much as if - oh yes.
\par 
