\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14290744 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 Only the gram}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13322343\charrsid4874471 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471  - the - the big - they had a - a big gram}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13322343\charrsid4874471 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 phone with a big horn to it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6752774 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 Would this be used to entertain everybody, would you sit around listening to music?
