\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6752774 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 This was when you'd got the two little ones.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14290744 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 Oh used to go to chapel then, used to take them with me on a - I used to really enjoy going for the hours - hour and a half's buting.

