\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6752774 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 Did Mr Marsh take part in any sport, go to the races, play cards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14290744 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 Oh no. No. They - we used to have a game dominoe}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11170647\charrsid4874471 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471  on the table sometime you know but - he wasn't - he was never a gambling - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6752774 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 Did he go out to pubs or clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14290744 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6752774 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 If they had a drink they would have it in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14290744 ET  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 I don't remember them having any - they used to keep the drink in the house for visitors but they never - never had any.
\par 
