\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6752774 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 She didn't belong to women}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11170647\charrsid4874471 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
