\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6752774 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10570170\charrsid4874471 Did she work for any charities or sit on committees or anything?
